room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by MindTrap Escape Room in Temecula
room_address: 26780 Ynez Ct Suite C Temecula, CA 92591
room_description: Can you feel the fever?! El Dorado county is hiding the richest secrets of the country right below the surface. Kanaka Jack is rumored to know the location of a hidden mine – finding it will make you rich beyond your wildest dreams! This is an escape game with an explosive secret that will bring the whole family together. Raid Jack’s cabin, unlock the entrance to his hidden mine, and blast your way out!
